{"tid":2446383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國自煮研發顯卡來了  性能超越GT710 厲害了我的國","createTime":"2021-03-14T11:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:23:00.000Z","uid":391580,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"c7d1b6a723491b2879a0de7326ee114f7b0e616c","tid":2446383,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"最新款JM7210顯卡是景嘉微在2020年底推出的一款我國自主研發生產的半高半長尺寸商用顯卡，最大功耗15W，不需要外接供電；28nm制程，核心頻率1200Mhz，顯存頻率最高1066Mhz；插槽支持PCIE2.0 X8/X4/X2/X1，輸出接口為VGA和HDMI。按照官方說法，該顯卡具備H.264、VC-1、VP8、MPEG2和MPEG4硬件解碼能力。<br />\n<br />\n比舊款JM7200性能提升五成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmetBRV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmetBRV.jpg&h=3debd2cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在景嘉威官方網站上目前列出的最强GPU為JM7200，該GPU依然基于中芯國際28nm CMOS工藝，支持4K超高清顯示或10屏同時輸出。像素填充率為像素填充率為5.2Gpixels/s，相當于GT710的34%；紋理填充率10.4GT/s，相當于GT710的163%，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">總體性能預計接近目前的辦公顯卡GT710。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cc2de00279b5f8a70c9f52c33a1f42e706f9ee55","tid":2446383,"uid":391580,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"差距唔係好大啫，同外國高端顯卡都係差幾十倍，好快就追得上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3iOaQdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3iOaQdj.jpg&h=ceb0e5d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74bbd4a55e48e01271797b069f5534f57e38b86c","tid":2446383,"uid":144735,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"一掘礦即燒"},{"pid":"255e82c5fd961bd15a972fe372865a8f9226d9fc","tid":2446383,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:15:28.000Z","msg":"Memory 1066MHz <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DDR2?"},{"pid":"330ccc11e3554724a5f693dee2d5d68047483f07","tid":2446383,"uid":61589,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:16:28.000Z","msg":"夠哂玩接龍/踩地雷喇<img src=\"/asse